step_data.thought:
I've been tasked with changing the map display by accessing the Layers options, and I've successfully done this multiple times:

1. I opened the Layers menu by clicking on the 'Layers' link
2. I changed the base map from Standard to CyclOSM
3. I checked the status of the Public GPS Traces overlay (which was already enabled)
4. I changed the base map to Humanitarian
5. I changed the base map to ÖPNVKarte

I've demonstrated multiple ways to change the map display through the Layers menu, including switching between different base maps and checking overlay options. The task has been successfully completed.

Now I should send a concise message to the user to inform them that the task is complete and summarize what was done.
